# Tools Used

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| MXToolbox | Verify SPF, DKIM, DMARC, DNS, and mail server configuration |
| VirusTotal | Check URL reputation and identify malicious indicators |
| urlscan.io | Analyze URLs and inspect webpage behavior |
| AbuseIPDB | Verify IP reputation and identify malicious IP addresses |

These tools were used to support the technical analysis wherever applicable during the investigation.
